title: Lombardi's Week 4 Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 314)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss the Chiefs' comeback and the Broncos' collapse on 'Monday Night Football' and Week 4 standouts. Then they give out some weekly awards.
